This is my favorite comic strip app on the Market, and I don't believe anything else even comes close to how good this app is at creating comic strips.  The app is constantly updated, and each update just makes it better and better!  But the very best thing to me, is the amazing support that this developer delivers to his customers. Previously the app had been protected, which I've always found to be an incredibly futile thing. But basically what that meant is that people like myself, who like to use backup apps to back up each version of any app on our device, were left without any way of doing so, short of rooting my device. I asked if the developer could remove the protection so I could update the app and back it up, and he not only did that, but he was extremely helpful and very friendly about doing it. This level of customer support that this developer provides, well it's what all Android developers should strive to achieve with their customers.  If you're looking for an app to create quality comic strips with, look no further. And don't even touch that Create A Comic app, it's malware, literally.
